data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT AND NOW OFFERING A $3,000 INCENTIVE to replace the carpet. Stunning ranch in Perry! 4 bedroom, 2 bath home features luxury vinyl plank throughout the common areas, soaring ceiling and fireplace in the living room, open concept floor plan, and formal dining room with elegant coffered ceiling - perfect for entertaining! The galley kitchen is light, bright, and boasts wood-like tile floor, granite counters, tile backsplash, breakfast area, and matching stainless steel appliance package - any chef's dream! Relax in the luxurious primary suite featuring tray ceiling, oversized dual vanity, walk-in closet, and garden tub with separate shower stall. Conveniently located, enjoy ease of access to local shopping, restaurants, and so much more! This one is a must see!
